SUMMARY: Free Estate Planning Seminar
DESCRIPTION:AT THIS COMPLIMENTARY PRESENTATION\, WE WILL DISCUSS SEVERAL 
 TOPICS INCLUDING:\n\n  * One Big Beautiful Bill Act: How the new tax law 
 may impact trusts\, estate planning\, and family succession strategies.\n
   * Wills and Living Trusts: Learn the advantages and disadvantages to bo
 th.\n  * Asset Protection: How to protect your assets and your family’s i
 nheritance from creditors\, divorce\, and lawsuits.\n  * Long Term Care P
 lanning: How to avoid losing your life savings.\n  * Next Spouse Protecti
 on: How to protect your assets from your surviving spouse’s next spouse.\
 n  * Probate: What is it and how to prevent it.\n  * Estate Taxes: What a
 re they\, and how to minimize or eliminate.\n  * Gifting to Children: How
  and when to gift your assets and why putting property in children’s name
 s may be a mistake.\n  * Special Needs: How to provide for special needs 
 (disabled) children and grandchildren.\n  * Legacy Planning: Good plannin
 g involves more than money. Learn some powerful tools to help instill imp
 ortant values in younger generation family members.\n  * And much\, much 
 more…
CATEGORIES:
