BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup: Rebel Craft Collective": "https://www.meetup.com/the-rebel-craft-collective/events/313260328/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_rebel_craft
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Rebel Craft Collective
UID:event_313260328@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260313T002913Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260312T173000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260312T193000
SUMMARY:Happy Hour Crafts
DESCRIPTION:The Rebel Craft Collective\nWine + tasty snacks + your latest project and a friendly group of likeminded crafters... what better way to unwind? Come join us!\n\nThis is a relaxed\, drop-in-friendly event. Come when you can\, leave when you must. Newcomers and occasional-comers are always welcome!\n\n**What do we mean by “crafts”?**\nWhatever “craft” means to you! And whatever is portable enough to bring to a wine bar. Knitting\, crochet\, and other fiber arts are most common\, but we have also warmly welcomed people who sketch\, color\, embroider\, bead\, and more. If your craft isn’t portable\, we will happily ooh and aah over photos of your work-in-progress\, or chat about your plans for your next project.\n\n**Health & Safety**\nMasks are very welcome\, and nobody will pressure you to eat or drink. If the weather is nice\, we will try to sit outside. If you aren’t eating/drinking during the event\, please consider ordering some of La Dolce Vita’s delicious food to-go\, in order to help support our gracious\, long-time venue.\n\n**Parking**\nParking in downtown Petaluma is free\, but street parking has a strictly enforced 2 hour limit until 6pm. To park for longer\, try the nearest garage:\n\n* The Second Street Garage entrance is located on C Street between First and Second Streets. It's all day parking on every level and a short walk to La Dolce Vita.\n\n**Ages**\nIt's a wine bar\, so this event is for adult crafters (though you're certainly not required to drink wine!). We’re okay with babes-in-arms if you are\, but this is not the right setting for wee crafters who are moving about on their own.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/the-rebel-craft-collective/events/313260328/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260208T041452Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260208T041452Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/a/2/b/3/600_527801651.jpeg
END:VEVENT
