SUMMARY: Macrame & Mixology Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Let's knot miss this one!\n\nNew Projects Every Month!\n\n**M
 ixology & Macramé Workshop**\n\n*Beginner Friendly – Kid Friendly – Socia
 l Craft Experience w/ Katherine Bergin\n\n*Join us for a creative and rel
 axing afternoon at our Mixology & Macramé Workshop! Learn to craft differ
 ent macramé pieces of your own while enjoying a drink in our cozy Barrel 
 Room @ Griffo Distillery. This is the perfect opportunity to unwind\, con
 nect\, and take home a handmade creation! See you Saturdays!\n\n**What's 
 Happening: Mixology & Macramé Workshop\n\n**Who's Cooking: Pizza 909\n\n*
 *Where: Griffo Distillery Tasting Bar\n\n**When: 2nd Saturdays of Every M
 onth - 2:30-4:30 PM\n\n**Workshop Highlights:**\nLearn step-by-step how t
 o craft a beautiful macramé piece to take home. All materials will be pro
 vided\, so just bring your creativity!\n\n*Past projects include: Plant h
 angers\, wall hangings\, coasters\, and more!\n\n**Relaxing Atmosphere:**
  Enjoy specialty cocktails crafted with Griffo's award-winning spirits wh
 ile you create.\n\n**Kid-Friendly Fun:** This workshop is beginner-friend
 ly and open to all ages\, making it a great activity for families\, frien
 ds\, or solo attendees.\n\n**Cost of Admission:**\n\n- $40 – Pay upon Arr
 ival\n\nSpace is limited\, so RSVP early to ensure your spot at the table
 .
