SUMMARY:Join us for Guided Buddhist Meditation and time for questions
DESCRIPTION:Meditate with a Monk in Sonoma County\nNew and experienced meditators are welcome. We will start with direct guidance to begin the practice and allow time to experience the silence of meditation on your own. There will be time at the end for your questions regarding meditation practice.\n\nYou may stay on for a potluck meal at 11:00 am. Welcome to bring a dish to share.\n\nThis is followed by Sutta Study program from 1:00 to 2:30 pm.\n\nWe meet outdoors in the Dhammadharini Monastery Garden in the Sala Pavillion\, as long as conducive weather lasts.\n\nCome in person\, or register at [here](https://www.dhammadharini.net/event-details/sunday-morning-guided-meditation-questions-2) to attend online
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/meditate-with-a-monk-in-sonoma-county/events/313493742/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260223T174611Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260223T174611Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
