DESCRIPTION:Get groovy at Griffo!\n\nGriffo is excited to welcome Fire Up
 !\, a Bay Area Tribute to the Garcia Saunders Songbook. This rotating cas
 t of players will have you transported with the first tune. Pizza 909 wil
 l be slinging Artisenal pies all day while the Griffo crew serves up deli
 cious cocktails from our ever rotating menu! Don't miss this homage to an
  era of music that never goes out of style! See you Sundays!\n\nWho's Pla
 ying: Fire Up!\n\nWho's Cooking: Pizza 909\n\nWhen: Sunday\, March 15th -
  Doors @ 1 pm\n\nWhere: Griffo Distillery\n\nPlease RSVP for this FREE\, 
 All Ages Event. Space is Limited.\n\nAbout the Band:\n\nFire up! Is a tri
 bute band interpreting the Jerry Garcia “Legion of Mary” era. Fire Up! is
  branded as “Songs from the Garcia – Saunders songbook." For note\, Fire 
 Up! is a name of a Garcia Saunders studio album\, https://open.spotify.co
 m/album/2b85gbWiMbAg3cvSUTMIBp https://open.spotify.com/album/2b85gbWiMbA
 g3cvSUTMIBp\n\nOur project is funky\, bluesy\, Jamy\, RnB\, and Jazzy wit
 h an emphasis on the Hammond organ.One might say “Ballroom brawling\, bab
 y making music\, modeled after the 1972 – 1975 Legion of Mary era. It is 
 different than what you hear from other JGB bands who focus on more of th
 e 80’s and 90’s gospel Jerry era.
