CREATED:20260106T203357Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260106T203357Z
UID:10002506-1773685800-1773698400@bigeasypetaluma.com
SUMMARY:The North Bay Get Down (Free Monthly Funk Jam)
DESCRIPTION:THE BEST MONDAY NIGHT IN THE NORTH BAY! 3rd Monday Each Month. This is a live monthly funk jam and dance party for musicians and music lovers of all kinds! Each month features a DJ\, then a rotating “House Band” of the top musicians\, followed by a curated/open jam – all music is improvised on the spot for a community funk dance party. Great live music\, dancing\, drinks\, and community vibes. Hosted by Ethan Schiff! \n6:30pm: Doors + Live DJ\n7:15 (ish): House Band Jam\n8-10pm: Curated/Open Jam \n*3rd Monday Every Month — Upcoming: Mar 16\, April 20\n*Follow @NorthBayGetDown on Instagram for real-time updates
URL:https://bigeasypetaluma.com/event/the-north-bay-get-down-free-monthly-funk-jam-5/
LOCATION:The Big Easy\, 128 American Alley\, Petaluma\, CA\, 94952\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://bigeasypetaluma.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/2026-2.png
END:VEVENT
