DESCRIPTION:This St. Patrick’s Day\, grab your best (green) dancin' shoes
  and come on down to WonderStump!\nPardon the Interruption https://www.pt
 imusic.com/ serves up ska-fueled funk\, rock\, reggae\, soul\, and upbeat
  jams-- turning the night into a full-body celebration. High spirits\, ha
 ppy feet\, and serious bounce guaranteed!\n\nWonderStump is an intentiona
 lly designed space for movement and flow. Enjoy the full-room energy with
 out the crush of an overpacked venue! Creative attire encouraged\, immers
 ive surprises in store\, light snacks and bevvies available for purchase.
 \n\nDoors at 6:30\, music at 7-- with special guests opening ✨\n\n$20 pre
 sale or hit us with $25 at the door 😎
CATEGORIES:Live-music,Dance-Music,Funk-Music,St-Patricks-Day
