SUMMARY:Beginners in The Work of Byron Katie: Newcomers Welcome
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream (CA)\nA free Zoom meditation session designed with newcomers in mind. Sessions will include at least one hour of facilitation (meditation) and there is room for questions and answers throughout. If you're curious about The Work\, you're invited to join!\n\nSee you there!\n\nPlease be aware that sessions will close if no members have joined after 10 minutes.\n\n**To book a free introductory private session with Emrys\, [click here](https://calendly.com/mindfulnesswithemrys/onehoursession)[.](https://mindfulnesswithemrys.business.site/)**\n\nEmrys also organises a free Work of Byron Katie Meetup group. Visit: [https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree](https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree/)\n\n*Find out more about Emrys [here](https://mindfulnesswithemrys.business.site/)[.](http://linktr.ee/theworkrunsfree)*
