DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260321T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260321T100000
SUMMARY:Awaken Yoga @ Hotel Petaluma
DESCRIPTION:Nourish 108 Ayurveda & Yoga\nJoin me for 60 minutes of nourishing morning yoga in the serene Brooklyn Ballroom at the Hotel Petaluma. While I am here to offer a sequence of poses\, this practice is yours to give your mind and body what it needs. Please bring your own yoga mat and any props you may need (strap\, block\, bolster\, blanket) and arrive a few minutes early to get situated. Extra mats available for hotel guests.\n\nAll levels welcome!\n\nDrop in is $18\, class passes available\, FREE for hotel guests. Sign up through the calendar at [www.nourish108.com/classes](www.nourish108.com/classes) or hotel front desk if you are a guest. Pay by credit/debit in advance or cash/Venmo on-site.\n\nI look forward to seeing you on your mat!
