DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260322T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260322T100000
SUMMARY:Join us for Guided Buddhist Meditation and time for questions
DESCRIPTION:Meditate with a Monk in Sonoma County\nNew and experienced meditators are welcome. We will start with direct guidance to begin the practice and allow time to experience the silence of meditation on your own. There will be time at the end for your questions regarding meditation practice.\n\nYou may stay on for a potluck meal at 11:00 am. Welcome to bring a dish to share.\n\nThis is followed by Sutta Study program from 1:00 to 2:30 pm.\n\nWe meet outdoors in the Dhammadharini Monastery Garden in the Sala Pavillion\, as long as conducive weather lasts.\n\nCome in person\, or register at [here](https://www.dhammadharini.net/event-details/sunday-morning-guided-meditation-questions-2) to attend online
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/meditate-with-a-monk-in-sonoma-county/events/313605186/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260302T180303Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260302T180303Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/4/f/5/2/600_513320306.jpeg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup Meditate Monk": "https://www.meetup.com/meditate-with-a-monk-in-sonoma-county/events/313605311/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_meditate_monk
X-SOURCE:Meetup Meditate Monk
UID:event_313605311@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260313T002916Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260322T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260322T100000
SUMMARY:Mindfulness Sunday Meditation: Cultivating Consciousness
DESCRIPTION:Meditate with a Monk in Sonoma County\nJoin us for a transformative workshop on mindfulness meditation and cultivating consciousness. Dive deep into the teachings of Theravada Buddhism\, focusing on insight meditation to develop a clear understanding of the nature of the mind and consciousness. This workshop will include guided meditation sessions to help you strengthen your meditation practice and cultivate mindfulness in your daily life. Whether you are a beginner or an experienced meditator\, this workshop offers a welcoming space to explore the depths of your own consciousness and enhance your spiritual journey. Come together with like-minded individuals to deepen your practice and connect with the wisdom of Theravada Buddhism\, and provide an opportunity to deepen mindfulness\, wisdom\, and inner stillness.\nOur sessions are led by Bhikkhunis closely associated with our Dhammadharini Sangha. Check out the [recording from the past event](https://youtube.com/live/s07U2kzWoWk?feature=share) on our YouTube channel.\nYou’re also welcome to join us in person at Dhammadharini Monastery\, in the peaceful setting of our outdoor Dana Sala Pavilion\nRegister for this event on Dhammadharini's website to receive the address:\n[https://www.dhammadharini.net/event-details/sunday-morning-guided-meditation-questions-2](https://www.dhammadharini.net/event-details/sunday-morning-guided-meditation-questions-2)\nCheck out the sangha website at\n[https://www.dhammadharini.net](https://www.dhammadharini.net/)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/meditate-with-a-monk-in-sonoma-county/events/313605311/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260302T180456Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260302T180456Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/b/3/7/8/600_530865944.jpeg
END:VEVENT
