SUMMARY:Read and discuss the teachings of the Buddha
DESCRIPTION:Meditate with a Monk in Sonoma County\nWe study the early Buddhist texts by reading aloud and discussing. The reading will be announced each week\n\n1:00pm. Meditation\n1:15-2:30pm. Sutta reading and discussion\n\nYou may come early for a potluck meal at 11:00 am. Welcome to bring a dish to share.\n\nWe meet outdoors in the Dhammadharini Monastery's Garden in the Sala Pavillion\, as long as conducive weather lasts.\n\nCome in person\, or register at [here](https://www.dhammadharini.net/event-details/sunday-morning-guided-meditation-questions-2) to attend online
