DTSTAMP:20260313T002913Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260324T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260324T193000
SUMMARY:Awakening Awareness: Embracing This Moment
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream (CA)\nA session inspired by Eckhart Tolle's practices. Feel free to join as we get still and practise presence within this moment. We will discuss and observe the obstacles that\, seemingly\, block us from being present and bring awareness to our unconsciousness in a safe\, inclusive and affirming way.\n\nSessions are suitable for newcomers\, those experienced in Tolle's teaching and anyone wishing to remain completely anonymous.\n\nSee you there!\n\nPlease be aware that sessions will close if no members have joined after 10 minutes.\n\nEmrys has been passionate about mindfulness since 2010 and since 2021 he has been organising free\, weekly online meditation groups. For more information on his free Work of Byron Katie online mediation group\, visit [this Meetup Group link](https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree/).
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/mindfulnesspetaluma/events/313644290/
