DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260325T200000
SUMMARY:Figure Drawing Night at Suite G Studio!
DESCRIPTION:Petaluma Figure Drawing Meetup Group\nJoin us for an evening of creativity and inspiration at the Petaluma Figure Drawing Meetup Group's Figure Drawing Night at Suite G Studio! Whether you're a seasoned artist or just starting out\, this event is the perfect opportunity to hone your skills\, meet fellow artists\, and immerse yourself in the world of figurative painting. Our life drawing sessions are open to artists and art lovers of all levels\, so don't be shy to join us and express your creativity on paper. We provide a supportive and encouraging environment where everyone can feel comfortable exploring their artistic talents.\n\n[BECOME A MEMBER](https://www.suitegstudio.com/artist-resources) of Suite G Studio for $40/month. Or RSVP by sending $25 to @suiteg on Venmo or email suitegstudio620@gmail.com\n\nBe prepared for an evening filled with sketching\, painting\, and drawing as we focus on capturing the human form in all its beauty and complexity. This event is a great opportunity to practice your figure drawing techniques and unleash your artistic potential. Whether you prefer using pencils\, charcoal\, pastels\, or paint\, there's something for everyone at our Figure Drawing Night. Come and be a part of our community of artists dedicated to celebrating and expressing the beauty of life through art.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/petaluma-figure-drawing-meetup-group/events/313760335/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
