X-SOURCE-URLS:{"SRJC Petaluma Campus": "https://calendar.santarosa.edu/event/16533-finding-women-in-historical-records"}
X-SOURCE-ID:srjc_petaluma
X-SOURCE:SRJC Petaluma Campus
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260326T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260326T130000
LOCATION:Zoom
SUMMARY:Finding Women in Historical Records
DESCRIPTION:Presenter: Denise BeesonJoin the Zoom here! (https://santaros
 a-edu.zoom.us/j/87117554258)&#160\;  Meeting ID: 871 1755 4258Event Descr
 iption: How many of your genealogy search challenges involve Female ances
 tors? Knowing our Female ancestors hinges upon knowing her maiden name\, 
 but there are few records of her\, and almost none that contain her maide
 n name. Believe it or not\, there's no record set that even focuses speci
 fically on women! So\, you need to be strategic in your search. Join me t
 o learn how to find your Female ancestor(s)!  For more information\, visi
 t SRJC's Women's History Month website (https://events.santarosa.edu/womx
 ns-history-month-2026).
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Presenter: Denise Beeson</p><p><a href=
 "https://santarosa-edu.zoom.us/j/87117554258" target="_blank" rel="noopen
 er">Join the Zoom here!</a>&#160\;</p><p>  Meeting ID: 871 1755 4258</p><
 p><strong>Event Description</strong>: How many of your genealogy search c
 hallenges involve Female ancestors? Knowing our Female ancestors hinges u
 pon knowing her maiden name\, but there are few records of her\, and almo
 st none that contain her maiden name. Believe it or not\, there's no reco
 rd set that even focuses specifically on women! So\, you need to be strat
 egic in your search. Join me to learn how to find your Female ancestor(s)
 !</p><p>  For more information\, visit <a href="https://events.santarosa.
 edu/womxns-history-month-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SRJC's Wome
 n's History Month website</a>.</p>
