SUMMARY:Bennett Friedman Quartet
DESCRIPTION:The Music Department of Santa Rosa Junior College presents a 
 jazz concert by the Bennett Friedman Quartet on Thursday\, April 2\, at 7
 :30 PM in Newman Auditorium on the SRJC campus. Guitarist Randy Vincent\,
  bassist Jeff Denson\, and drummer Kendrick Freeman will be featured.  Th
 e quartet will perform "Take Five" by Paul Desmond\, compositions of Bobb
 y Hutcherson\, Wayne Shorter\, and others.  General admission is $15\, an
 d $10 for students and seniors. Parking on campus is $4. Proceeds from th
 e concert benefit the SRJC Foundation Jazz Studies Fund.Visit SRJC's Musi
 c Department website here! (https://music.santarosa.edu/events)
