SUMMARY:Artist Reception - Jerrold Ballaine: Land and Sea
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an artist reception to celebrate Northern Califor
 nia artist Jerrold "Jerry" Ballaine\, who has enjoyed a diverse and susta
 ined career\, including teaching at UC Berkeley. The reception will provi
 de a unique opportunity to engage directly with Mr. Ballaine. Academic De
 an Mary-Catherine Oxford will provide opening remarks. Artist and author 
 Jack Leissring will speak on behalf of Mr. Ballaine. Light refreshments w
 ill be served.&#160\;
