 r’s Butter & Egg Days Parade recognizes the farmers\, families\, immigra
 nts\, makers\, entrepreneurs\, and creatives whose hard work\, imagination
 \, and ingenuity reflect the enduring American Dream. This celebration als
 o pays respect to the Indigenous peoples who first stewarded this land\, t
 he courage of our founders\, and the dedication of the dairy and egg farmi
