LOCATION:Burbank Auditorium Main Stage Theatre - Santa Rosa Campus
SUMMARY:Hello Dolly! - The Musical - Bargain Show
DESCRIPTION:This musical adaptation of Thornton Wilder's hit play The Mat
 chmaker includes humor\, romance\, energetic dance\, and some of the grea
 test songs in music theatre history.  The romantic and comic exploits of 
 Dolly Gallagher Levi\, turn-of-the-century matchmaker and "woman who arra
 nges things\," are a thrill and highly entertaining to audiences.  Direct
 ed by Gina Alvarado  Book by Michael Stewart  Music and Lyrics by Jerry H
 erman  &#160\;  Location: Main Stage Theatre at Burbank Auditorium on San
 ta Rosa Campus.  Tickets: $15  &#160\;Buy tickets here! (https://srjc.uni
 versitytickets.com/w/event.aspx?id=1783)  SRJC Theatre Arts Website: http
 s://theatrearts.santarosa.edu/ (https://theatrearts.santarosa.edu/)&#160\
 ;
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  This musical adaptation of Thornton Wil
 der's hit play <em>The Matchmaker</em> includes humor\, romance\, energet
 ic dance\, and some of the greatest songs in music theatre history.<br />
   The romantic and comic exploits of Dolly Gallagher Levi\, turn-of-the-c
 entury matchmaker and "woman who arranges things\," are a thrill and high
 ly entertaining to audiences.</p><p>  Directed by Gina Alvarado<br />  Bo
 ok by Michael Stewart<br />  Music and Lyrics by Jerry Herman</p><p>  &#1
 60\;</p><p>  Location: Main Stage Theatre at Burbank Auditorium on Santa 
