SUMMARY:Light the Dream Business Making 101
DESCRIPTION:Undocumented Californians are building businesses\, and every
 one can learn from their effort. Whether you have papers or not. Whether 
 you want to launch something one day or support a friend who does. This s
 ession invites new ways of thinking about work\, creativity\, and contrib
 ution that helps neighbors. We'll look at entrepreneurial paths that make
  room for people who don't see themselves in grind culture\, and for thos
 e who want to build something meaningful\, sustainable\, and rooted in pu
 rpose.  &#160\;  SRJC Undocu • Immigrant • Dream Center invites you t
 o join these virtual professional development series designed for those w
 ho work with undocumented students.Register here! (https://events.zoom.us
 /ev/An2mq_9p0JQpRAYki5BLgRh9wjPS4D6XnMxqZEl2F3lcZU-z2nHz~AnlWoDIvcvd7J558
 i96u7TtP3SKeaUn8DtpFAZ1N2r67C0mC28hPlTz9iQ)  For more information\, visit
  the SRJC Undocu • Immigrant • Dream Center Website (https://dream.sa
 ntarosa.edu/workshops-events-2025-2026)
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Undocumented Californians are building 
 businesses\, and everyone can learn from their effort. Whether you have p
 apers or not. Whether you want to launch something one day or support a f
 riend who does. This session invites new ways of thinking about work\, cr
 eativity\, and contribution that helps neighbors. We'll look at entrepren
 eurial paths that make room for people who don't see themselves in grind 
 culture\, and for those who want to build something meaningful\, sustaina
 ble\, and rooted in purpose.</p><p>  &#160\;</p><p>  SRJC Undocu • Immi
 grant • Dream Center invites you to join these virtual professional dev
 elopment series designed for those who work with undocumented students.</
 p><p><a href="https://events.zoom.us/ev/An2mq_9p0JQpRAYki5BLgRh9wjPS4D6Xn
 MxqZEl2F3lcZU-z2nHz~AnlWoDIvcvd7J558i96u7TtP3SKeaUn8DtpFAZ1N2r67C0mC28hPl
 Tz9iQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Register here!</a></p><p>  For more
  information\, visit the <a href="https://dream.santarosa.edu/workshops-e
 vents-2025-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SRJC Undocu • Immigrant
  • Dream Center Website</a></p>
