 or canopy\, between buildings 400 &amp\; 500.  For faster check-in\, down
 load the "MySRJC App" and register with Redwood Empire Food Bank prior to
  the event.  Don't forget to bring your own grocery bags\, some will be p
 rovided on a first come first serve basis.  Can't make it? Leftover produ
 ce and other items are moved to the Welcome &amp\; Connect Center after e
 ach event.
