 we've got veggie stuff too!\n\nCome on out to make some music\, shake you
 r hips\, sip on Griffo's ever-rotating cocktail menu\, and keep the jam a
 live! See you at Thursdays Griffo Distillery! 🎸🥁🎷🍸 #ScottStreetGinJam
  #LiveMusic #GriffoDistillery\n\nAs featured in The Bohemian & Argus Cour
 rier - Thank You Don Lewis & David Templeton!!\n\nPlease RSVP for this FR
 EE\, All Ages Event!
